OL,6,FA girl with a severe dairy allergy
OL,7,Fdied after drinking a Costa Coffee hot
OL,8,Fchocolate in what was a "failure to
OL,9,Ffollow the processes in place to
OL,10,Fdiscuss allergies", an inquest has
OL,11,Fconcluded.
OL,13,FAssistant coroner Dr Shirley Radcliffe
OL,14,Fsaid there had been a "failure of
OL,15,Fcommunication" between the coffee shop
OL,16,Fstaff and Hannah Jacobs' mother.
OL,18,FThe 13-year-old died within hours of
OL,19,Fdrinking the hot chocolate on February
OL,20,F8, 2023, the East London Coroner's
OL,21,FCourt was told.
