OL,6,FThe coroner also noted that on the day
OL,7,Fof her death "neither Hannah or her
OL,8,Fmother were carrying an Epipen that
OL,9,Fhad been prescribed."
OL,11,FA member of Ms Duyile's legal team
OL,12,Fread a statement outside East London
OL,13,Fcoroner's court on her behalf which
OL,14,Fsaid: "Better awareness is really
OL,15,Fneeded in these industries and across
OL,16,Fsociety of the symptoms of anaphylaxis.
OL,18,F"Allowing people who serve food and
OL,19,Fdrinks to retake an allergy training
OL,20,Ftest for 20 times is not acceptable.
