OL,6,FAfter the inquest concluded Costa
OL,7,FCoffee released a statement calling Ms
OL,8,FJabos's death a "tragedy."
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "The loss of
OL,11,FHannah is a tragedy, and our heartfelt
OL,12,Fthoughts remain with her family and
OL,13,Ffriends.
OL,15,F"Understanding how this awful
OL,16,Fsituation occurred is in the interest
OL,17,Fof everyone ` our franchise partners,
OL,18,Four customers, our team members, and
OL,19,Fthe communities of which we are a part.
